ee-handbook.png 2x"> <img data-src="https://img2.storyblok.com/328x0/filters:format(png):quality(75)/f/145847/1074x500/2550dc6ac4/employee-handbook.png" src="https://img2.storyblok.com/328x0/filters:format(png):blur(30):quality(30)/f/145847/1074x500/2550dc6ac4/employee-handbook.png" class="lazy w-full h-full object-cover"></picture> <!----> <!----></div> <div class="h-[24px] md:h-[60px]"></div> <div class="w-full px-[8px] md:px-[60px] lg:px-[120px]"><div class="w-full flex items-center"><div class="flex items-center mt-auto space-x-[16px] md:space-x-[24px]"><div class="bg-lavender max-w-[36px] max-h-[36px] md:max-w-[48px] md:max-h-[48px] overflow-hidden rounded-full inner-img:w-full inner-img:h-full inner-img:object-cover"><picture><source media="(min-width: 768px)" type="image/webp" data-srcset="https://img2.storyblok.com/48x0/filters:format(webp):quality(75)/f/145847/3801x3801/26589a905c/dde0e40e-4eea-4c92-8626-01a7ffd84e39_mary_isaeva_px.png 1x, https://img2.storyblok.com/96x0/filters:format(webp):quality(75)/f/145847/3801x3801/26589a905c/dde0e40e-4eea-4c92-8626-01a7ffd84e39_mary_isaeva_px.png 2x" srcset="https://img2.storyblok.com/48x0/filters:format(webp):blur(30):quality(30)/f/145847/3801x3801/26589a905c/dde0e40e-4eea-4c92-8626-01a7ffd84e39_mary_isaeva_px.png, https://img2.storyblok.com/96x0/filters:format(webp):blur(30):quality(30)/f/145847/3801x3801/26589a905c/dde0e40e-4eea-4c92-8626-01a7ffd84e39_mary_isaeva_px.png 2x"> <source media="(min-width: 768px)" data-srcset="https://img2.storyblok.com/48x0/filters:format(png):quality(75)/f/145847/3801x3801/26589a905c/dde0e40e-4eea-4c92-8626-01a7ffd84e39_mary_isaeva_px.png 1x, https://img2.storyblok.com/96x0/filters:format(png):quality(75)/f/145847/3801x3801/26589a905c/dde0e40e-4eea-4c92-8626-01a7ffd84e39_mary_isaeva_px.png 2x" srcset="https://img2.storyblok.com/48x0/filters:format(png):blur(30):quality(30)/f/145847/3801x3801/26589a905c/dde0e40e-4eea-4c92-8626-01a7ffd84e39_mary_isaeva_px.png, https://img2.storyblok.c