rose-headings:font-700 prose-headings:text-charcoal prose-h1:mb-[32px] prose-h1:mt-[48px] prose-h1:text-[34px] prose-h1:leading-[40px] prose-h1:tracking-[0.25px] md:prose-h1:text-[48px] md:prose-h1:leading-[56px] md:prose-h1:tracking-[0px] lg:prose-h1:text-[60px] lg:prose-h1:leading-[72px] prose-h2:text-[24px] prose-h2:leading-[32px] prose-h2:tracking-[0px] prose-h2:mt-[48px] prose-h2:mb-[24px] md:prose-h2:text-[34px] md:prose-h2:leading-[40px] md:prose-h2:tracking-[0.25px] lg:prose-h2:text-[40px] lg:prose-h2:leading-[48px] lg:prose-h2:tracking-[0px] prose-h3:text-[20px] prose-h3:leading-[32px] prose-h3:tracking-[0.15px] prose-h3:mb-[20px] md:prose-h3:text-[24px] md:prose-h3:leading-[32px] md:prose-h3:tracking-[0px] prose-p:m-0 prose-p:font-500 prose-p:text-charcoal prose-p:text-[14px] prose-p:leading-[24px] prose-p:tracking-[0.1px] prose-p:mb-[20px] md:prose-p:text-[16px] md:prose-p:leading-[32px] md:prose-p:tracking-[0.15px] prose-a:text-blue prose-strong:font-700 prose-blockquote:border-none prose-blockquote:relative prose-p:before:content-[] prose-blockquote:not-italic prose-blockquote:m-0 prose-blockquote:p-[8px_0px_8px_16px] md:prose-blockquote:p-[8px_0px_8px_26px] prose-blockquote:before:absolute prose-blockquote:before:inset-0 prose-blockquote:before:w-[4px] prose-blockquote:before:bg-blue prose-blockquote:before:rounded-full prose-blockquote:before:left-0 md:prose-blockquote:before:w-[6px] prose-ol:pl-[16px] prose-ol:mb-[20px] prose-ol:list-decimal md:prose-ol:pl-[26px] prose-li:marker:proportional-nums prose-ul:pl-[16px] prose-ul:mb-[20px] prose-ul:list-disc md:prose-ul:pl-[26px] prose-li:font-500 prose-li:text-charcoal prose-li:text-[16px] prose-li:leading-[32px] prose-li:m-0 prose-li:p-0 prose-table:table-fixed prose-table:border-[0px] prose-table:text-charcoal prose-table:text-[14px] prose-table:leading-[24px] md:prose-table:text-[16px] prose-tr:grid prose-tr:divide-y-[3px] prose-tr:divide-lavender prose-tr:border-[0px] sm:prose-tr:border-[3px] sm:prose-tr:border-lavender sm:prose-tr:table-row prose-td:p-[32px] sm:prose-td:border-[3px] sm:prose-td:border-lavender prose-th:p-[32px] empty:prose-th:hidden sm:empty:prose-th:table-cell sm:prose-th:border-[3px] sm:prose-th:border-lavender prose-thead:border-[3px] prose-thead:border-lavender prose-tbody:border-[3px] prose-tbody:border-lavender prose-tbody:divide-y-[3px] prose-tbody:divide-lavender"><h2 id="whatarethebenefitsofhavingan&#xA0;employeehandbook">What Are The Benefits Of Having An&#xA0;Employee Handbook?</h2>
<p>By now, you&#x2019;ll be aware that one of the top <strong>benefits of having an&#xA0;employee handbook</strong>&#xA0;is that it&#x2019;s a simple yet effective way to welcome&#xA0;new hires&#xA0;with open arms. But the benefits don&#x2019;t stop there:</p>
<ul>
<li>A <strong>full overview of&#xA0;company culture</strong>&#xA0;lets&#xA0;new hires&#xA0;know what they can look forward to.</li>
<li>It builds a <strong>strong and positiv</strong>e&#xA0;employment relationship&#xA0;from the get-go.</li>
<li>You can <strong>clarify expectations</strong> of their employment which means that misunderstandings are greatly reduced.</li>
<li>It&#x2019;s a <strong>simple way</strong> to show what they can expect from the company and their management teams.</li>
<li>Employees will know what <strong>behaviours are rewarded</strong> so are more likely to replicate them in their work.</li>
<li>It <strong>protects</strong> you, your company, and the employees themselves.</li>
<li>They&#x2019;re easy to create with the&#xA0;<a href="https://flair.hr/en/try-for-free" rel="noopener">Flair&#xA0;employee handbook&#xA0;template</a>, so it won&#x2019;t take up much of your time.</li>
</ul>
<h2 id="conclusion">Conclusion</h2>
<p>An&#xA0;employee handbook&#xA0;comes in many forms. Whether you decide to get creative or stick to a strong business format, a manual for your employee is essential. They&#x2019;re a <strong>powerful tool for consistent communication</strong> across any size company. And they allow employees to start off on the right foot and continue that attitude throughout their employment.</p>
<p>So how you decide to convey the information is down to your preference and company attitude. But the importance of an&#xA0;employee handbook&#xA0;is universal. It&#x2019;s absolutely crucial that you have one and that your <strong>employees read, understand, and sign it</strong>.</p>
<p>Here at&#xA0;<a href="/en/" rel="noopener">Flair</a>, we understand the importance of a <strong>robust&#xA0;employee handbook</strong>. And our skills don&#x2019;t stop there. Take the time to check out the platform we&#x2019;ve lovingly built that&#x2019;ll make your existing processes even more efficient.</p>
